high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up a tomato in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward then turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the nearest tomato from the sink
Turn around and walk over to the microwave
Heat the tomato in the microwave then remove it
Turn around and walk back to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Pick the tomato that is closest up from the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and then take the tomato out again.
Go right and right again to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.
